# Comparable vs Comparator

### Comparable

Natural ordering.

```java
Collections.sort(list);
```

---

### Comparator

Custom sorting.

```java
Collections.sort(list, (a,b) -> b-a);
```

Useful for:

- Objects
- Descending Order
- Multi-level Sorting

