# Time Complexity Summary

| Data Structure | Insert | Search | Delete |
|---------------|--------|--------|--------|
| ArrayList | O(1)* | O(1) | O(n) |
| LinkedList | O(1)** | O(n) | O(1)** |
| Stack | O(1) | O(1) | O(1) |
| Queue | O(1) | O(1) | O(1) |
| PriorityQueue | O(log n) | O(1)*** | O(log n) |
| HashSet | O(1) | O(1) | O(1) |
| TreeSet | O(log n) | O(log n) | O(log n) |
| HashMap | O(1) | O(1) | O(1) |
| TreeMap | O(log n) | O(log n) | O(log n) |

\* Amortized at the end.  
\** At known ends (head/tail).  
\*** `peek()` only; arbitrary search is O(n).

