# Common Mistakes

## 1. Using `==` for Strings

Wrong

```java
s1 == s2
```

Correct

```java
s1.equals(s2)
```

---

## 2. Using `HashMap` When Order is Needed

Use

```java
TreeMap
```

---

## 3. Forgetting Generics

Wrong

```java
ArrayList list = new ArrayList();
```

Correct

```java
ArrayList<Integer> list = new ArrayList<>();
```

---

## 4. Using `remove(int)` on `ArrayList<Integer>`

```java
list.remove(1);
```

Removes **index 1**, not the value `1`.

To remove the value:

```java
list.remove(Integer.valueOf(1));
```

